title: Ep - 36 - Catelynn Baltierra from MTV’s Teen Mom
description:
Catelynn Baltierra from MTV’s Teen Mom explains how MTV found her, the hardest part about exposing your life on TV, her postpartum depression, and whether she will expand her family. Luann de Lesseps’ hilarious ex-boyfriend Rey Bolic calls Kate from a café in Miami to discuss his infamous scene on Real Housewives of New York, and writer Ryan Bailey is forced to watch two episodes of this season’s The Voice.
